    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_001/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The card focuses narrowly on MS2 fingerprint generation, which is the first step of the MEMO workflow. The paper's scope is broader, covering the full MEMO method including sample comparison, clustering, and application to drug discovery. However, the fingerprint generation step is clearly described and central to the method.",
        "The card does not mention the two alternative workflows (MEMO from unaligned vs. aligned samples), which are both described in the paper and represent important variations in the fingerprint generation process."
      ],
      "asbval:n_drift_notes": 2,
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_001",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
