      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_003/001",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Documents are then aggregated by summing peaks and losses occurrences across spectra of a given sample to obtain the MEMO vector (Figure 1B). Samples' MEMO vectors can then be aligned to obtain a MEMO matrix (Figure 1C).",
      "asbval:note": "The paper describes MEMO vectors (samples) and their aggregation into a MEMO matrix with peaks and losses as features.",
