      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "First, MS2 spectra are filtered and binned using matchms and spec2vec packages: peaks and losses to the precursor of the spectrum are converted into words (i.e. peak@mz and loss@mz) and grouped into so-called documents",
