    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/ms2-fingerprint-distance-calculation/009",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Documents are then aggregated by summing peaks and losses occurrences across spectra of a given sample to obtain the MEMO vector... Samples' MEMO vectors can then be aligned to obtain a MEMO matrix... The distance matrices were computed using pdist function ('braycurtis' metric) from scipy package... scikit-bio (0.5.6) was used for PCoA computation on the resulting distance matrix",
