      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Parse mass spectrometry spectral data from common file formats (mzML, mzXML, MGF, msp, JSON) and validate metadata, peak lists, and precursor ion information to ensure data integrity before downstream processing. This is essential for MS/MS-based sample comparison workflows where",
